  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Plan for Communication stack relocation in Zeekr:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Current status: FR, CAN and LIN along with vDataHandler is in Core 0"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Goal: Move FR complete stack to Core 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Limitations:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "We cannot use RTE between COM and Application SWCs (Third party), which means complete application will be in Core 1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 1: FR stack to Core 1 and let vDataHandler and Com in Core 0"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20COM%20Sync/image2022-10-27_17-10-40.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore COM Sync/image2022-10-27_17-10-40.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Step 2: Move Com to Core 1, also the vDataHandler and application"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Prerequisite: INC multi core capability should be available"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Note:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For Diagnostic data from SoC we need a CDD in Core 0"
    }
  ],
